---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — Waldo Vanderhaeghen" description="How this site handles your data">
  <article class="legal">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <h2>Who is responsible</h2>
    <p>
      Waldo Vanderhaeghen, Berlin, Germany.<br />
      Contact: <a href="mailto:waldov86@gmail.com">waldov86@gmail.com</a>
    </p>

    <h2>What data is collected</h2>
    <p>
      This site uses Google Analytics 4 to understand how visitors find and read content.
      Analytics is only activated if you explicitly accept cookies. If you decline, no data is sent to Google.
    </p>
    <p>
      When analytics is active, Google Analytics collects: pages visited, time spent, referrer URL,
      browser type, and approximate country. No names, email addresses, or personally identifiable
      information are collected.
    </p>

    <h2>Google Analytics & Consent Mode v2</h2>
    <p>
      This site uses Google Consent Mode v2. Analytics storage is set to <strong>denied</strong> by default.
      It is only changed to <strong>granted</strong> when you click "Accept" in the cookie banner.
      Your choice is stored in your browser's localStorage and respected on return visits.
    </p>
    <p>
      Google Analytics data is processed by Google LLC. For more information, see
      <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
    <p>
      You have the right to access, correct, delete, or restrict processing of your personal data.
      You can withdraw consent at any time by clearing your browser's localStorage or by contacting me
      at <a href="mailto:waldov86@gmail.com">waldov86@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>No other tracking</h2>
    <p>
      This site uses no advertising trackers, no social media pixels, no third-party cookies beyond
      Google Analytics (and only when consented), and no server-side logging of visitor IP addresses.
    </p>

    <h2>Hosting</h2>
    <p>
      This site is hosted on <a href="https://vercel.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vercel</a>.
      Vercel may process access logs as part of its infrastructure. See
      <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vercel's Privacy Policy</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .legal {
    max-width: var(--prose-width);
    margin: 3rem auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
